headline: What Catalysts Are Shaping the Evolving Narrative for UnitedHealth?
summary: UnitedHealth Group has seen a modest uptick in its consensus analyst price target, rising from $333.42 to $342.58. This change comes as investors react to improved Medicare Advantage Star ratings, which has bolstered confidence in the company’s long-term prospects.
